title: Amar Akbar Anthony
subTitle: Three brothers, each raised in different religious households, reunite after many years in a chance encounter. They set out to take revenge on those responsible for separating them.

title: Shriman Shrimati
subTitle: Appalled by the numerous problems faced by middle-class families, a wealthy couple decide to forsake their luxuries and live among the common people to make a difference in society.

title: Nachnewale Gaanewale
subTitle: Two friends sing and dance at functions for a living and decide to get their respective children married to each other. To their dismay, the son refuses to comply.

title: Jaal
subTitle: Fate plays a cruel game when Shankar gets hired by a rich woman named Amita who bears an uncanny resemblance with Meenabai, the person who breaks his family apart.

title: Andolan
subTitle: Adarsh and Aniket are two brothers who study in the same college. However, when they graduate and plan to establish a career, both of them choose different paths and gradually drift apart.

title: Yeshwant
subTitle: Yeshwant, an honest police inspector, is framed and arrested for a murder. However, after being released from prison, he learns that his wife is having an affair.

title: Gabbar Is Back
subTitle: The city's administration wrongs Aditya, a commoner. To avenge his tragedy, he disguises himself as a vigilante, Gabbar, and teams up with honest government officers to expose the corrupt.

title: Itihaas
subTitle: Naina, who is betrothed to an influential man, falls in love and elopes with Karan, the son of an employee of her fiance. Soon, bounty hunters start hunting the duo to claim a hefty reward.

title: Ajnabee
subTitle: Raj and Priya befriend their new neighbours Vicky and Sonia. One day, Raj wakes up in Vicky's house and finds out that Sonia is killed and he is framed for it.

title: Ajnabee

title: Salaam Bombay!
subTitle: When a revengeful Krishna destroys his brother's motorbike, his mother asks him to return home only when he earns INR 500 to repair it. In a turn of events, he finds himself in a Bombay slum.

title: Roti
subTitle: Mangal Singh escapes prison and begins a new life, unknowingly befriending his victim's family. As he seeks redemption, his past catches up, compelling him to confront his previous misdeeds.

title: Chaand Ka Tukda
subTitle: Determined to fulfil his mother's final wish, a young NRI returns to India to find an ideal bride. However, things take a turn after he falls in love with a village belle.

title: Ittefaq
subTitle: Shiva, a professional hitman, is hired to eliminate an eyewitness to a murder. However, complications arise when he decides to protect the man he is hired to kill.

title: Kuch Kuch Hota Hai
subTitle: After reading the letter her mother had written for her before she died, Anjali decides to bring together her widowed father, Rahul, with his true love who is also named Anjali.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Suryavanshi
subTitle: An archaeologist digs up a secret underground palace, much to the dismay of the locals, who fear the consequences.

title: Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam
subTitle: A newly-wed man discovers that his wife is in love with another man and decides to unite them. Ignoring the ridicule he might have to face for this, he takes his wife to Italy in search of her love.

title: Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam

title: Qila
subTitle: When Amarnath's brother Jaganath is murdered, he sets out to investigate the case. However, things take a turn when the suspect list includes his sister-in-law and nephew.

title: Dekh Tamasha Dekh
subTitle: The death of a religiously ambiguous man in a rural Indian town leads to tensions between two factions of the Hindu and Muslim communities over the body.

title: Garam Masala
subTitle: A flirtatious photographer juggles three air hostesses behind his fiancee's back. However, the facade unravels when his friend-turned-enemy starts snooping around.

title: Dilwale
subTitle: Despite the family rivalry, Raj and Meera fall in love other but a misunderstanding causes them to part ways. Years later, fate brings them together when their siblings fall for each other.

title: Jaisi Karni Waisi Bharni
subTitle: A conniving son throws his aged parents out of the house. Years later, he meets the same fate when his son decides to teach him a lesson.

title: Mujrim
subTitle: Yashoda, a widow, brings up her children with love and honesty. However, she is disappointed when her son Shankar is arrested for breaking the law and disowns him.

title: Baghban
subTitle: Raj and Pooja live an upsetting life when their sons refuse to reciprocate their affections and take care of them.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fianc√© plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.
